(3339, 'Arilobe 30mg 20 f.c.tab.', 'اريلوب 30 مجم 20 قرص', '120', '160', 'Aripiprazole', 'Medisave developed', 'Tab', 'أقراص', 'مضاد للاكتئاب. يعالج مرض الذهان. يساعد في علاج حالات الهلوسة. يقوم بتحسين التركيز والتفكير بشكل إيجابي.', 'Psychiatric.antipsychotics', '30mg', 'Aripiprazole is indicated for the treatment of acute manic and mixed episodes associated with bipolar I disorder, irritability associated with autism spectrum disorder, schizophrenia, and Tourette''s disorder.[L45859] It is also used as an adjunctive treatment of major depressive disorder.[L45859 An injectable formulation of aripiprazole is indicated for agitation associated with schizophrenia or bipolar mania.[L45859] Finally, an extended-release, bimonthly injection formulation of aripiprazole is indicated for the treatment of adult schizophrenia and maintenance therapy for adult bipolar I disorder.[L46203]', '6225000349742', '', 1669, '2024-12-02', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP),
